s Website Type And Layout</h3><p>Defining your business goals will later appear via your site structure and overall design. Do you want to showcase your service through a clean landing page, build a complex e-commerce website, or start a blog about cats?</p><p>The acknowledgment of your business project targets and niche-specific requirements <em>(core features you should have on your page)</em> will help you to choose an appropriate template. At this point, you can check competitors to gain more insights on the topic.</p><p>Once youve considered your website type, its time to focus on your website design and layout  the structure determining the appearance of your content. These are just a few key points you can pay attention to while choosing a WordPress template:</p><ul><li>Overall user experience;</li><li>Easy navigation process;</li><li>Content width design type <em>(full-width or boxed width)</em>;</li><li>The placement of your logo;</li><li>Header and footer layout.</li></ul><p>Without a doubt, there are a lot more things to consider. For instance, underestimating the <a href=\"https://visualcomposer.com/blog/ultimate-guide-to-colors-and-color-palettes/\">importance of color palette</a> choice and sites typography can lead to visitors poor evaluation of your brand as a whole.</p><h3>Look For Flexible Customization</h3><p>Rich set of features and flexible customization options are useful to avoid yet another website effect. A personalized template will stand your brand among competitors.</p><p>However, the customization process shouldnt require a complete redesign.</p><p>A good practice is to choose the WordPress template that offers a wide variety of features from niche-specific to general ones for a wide range of fields. The rest is simple  you only need to eliminate elements you arent going to use.</p><p>The key to success here is opting for an easy-to-use content editing and built-in powerful tools to enhance your template. For that reason, all Visual Composer WordPress templates have a <a href=\"https://visualcomposer.com/features/drag-and-drop-website-builder/\">drag-and-drop</a> interface  the simplest way to edit your content without any coding skills needed.</p><h3>Choose Responsive And SEO-friendly Template</h3><p>Im sure you want to target as much wider audience as possible. With that in mind, consider having a responsive website a must, because more than half of your potential users will use mobile devices to interact with your site.</p><p>To make sure your site appears equally well on any device, all Visual Composer templates are mobile-friendly and come with an option to preview your layout on the most popular device types. In addition, there is mobile editing  the way to manage your content via phone or tablet.</p><p>Apart from responsiveness, another powerful tool to reach the audience is applying effective SEO techniques. In essence, striving for SEO-friendly templates helps you to rank higher and ensures fast page load time.</p><h3>Consider Support Availability</h3><p>While working with a WordPress template rarely requires some coding or designing skills, you want to be covered in case some technical or other issues arise.</p><p>So, customer support availability is highly important when choosing a WordPress template for your site. Fixing the issue should be a priority of your template supplier in the WordPress environment.</p><p>And Visual Composer templates fully match industry standards: you not only get the template, but also receive built-in professional customer and technical support, constant updates, and bug fixes. Besides, you can browse through comprehensive help tutorials or <a href=\"https://visualcomposer.com/contacts/\">ask pre-sales questions</a> to clarify things.</p><h2>Wrap-Up</h2><p>To summarize the guidelines on choosing the best WordPress website templates in 2020, opt for a high-quality and professionally-designed responsive template. Also, the ease of customization should be coupled with feature-rich assets to extend the template.</p><p>With that in mind, pick one of these Visual Composer templates and youll be good to go to create a beautiful WordPress site fast and easy.</p></div></div><div class=\"vce-button--style-basic-container vce-button--style-basic-container--align-center\"><span class=\"vce-button--style-basic-wrapper vce\" id=\"el-87c02e06\" data-vce-do-apply=\"margin el-87c02e06\"><a class=\"vce-button--style-basic vce-button--style-basic--border-square vce-button--style-basic--size-medium vce-button--style-basic--color-b-255-174-39--fff vce-button--style-basic--hover-color-b-27-71-160--fff\" href=\"https://visualcomposer.com/pricing/\" title=\"\" data-vce-do-apply=\"padding border background  el-87c02e06\">Get Your WordPress Template  Today</a></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://visualcomposer.com/blog/best-wordpress-templates-2020/\">Best WordPress Templates 2020</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://visualcomposer.com\">Visual Composer Website Builder</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://visualcomposer.com/blog/best-wordpress-templates-2020/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\